  <md:title>The First Law of Thermodynamics and Heat Engine Processes</md:title>
  <md:abstract><list>
<item>Describe the processes of a simple heat engine.</item>
<item>Explain the differences among the simple thermodynamic processes—isobaric, isochoric, isothermal, and adiabatic.</item>
<item>Explain the relationship between work done by a gas and change in its volume.</item>
</list></md:abstract>
